Admin-level access is required for updates.

options.description: ElevenLabs Webhook Handler for Dynamic Call Configuration This endpoint processes incoming webhook requests from ElevenLabs for voice calls. It retrieves the agent configuration from the database and returns a properly formatted response with all dynamic variables and configuration overrides. Enhanced features: - Improved context building with template engine - Dynamic tool configuration based on agent settings - Better performance with parallel data fetching - Enhanced caller personalization and history - Structured configuration management - Optimized prompt generation (behavioral guidance only, no redundant tool descriptions) - Data flow map:  docs/Data-mapping/sales-pitch-enhanced-data-flow.md - OBS: UPDATE CHANGES IN DATA FLOW MAP WHEN MAKING CHANGES HERE Optimization Notes (2025-10-01): - Tool parameter descriptions removed (already in /convai/tool_configs/*.json) - Only behavioral workflow guidance included in prompts - Deprecated variables cleaned up (system_prompt_bundle, default_event_id_for_tools) - Added user_id field for better analytics tracking - Added optional max_tokens support for response length control - Expected 15-20% prompt size reduction (~300-500 tokens saved per call) Response format follows: https://elevenlabs.io/docs/conversational-ai/guides/twilio/dynamic-calls.md https://elevenlabs.io/docs/conversational-ai/customization/personalization/dynamic-variables.md
